page.title: 10HOUSING - SUTTONS LANE AREA
page.content:
REPORT ON THE HOUSING IN THE SUTTONS LANE AREA - The most common tyoe of house in this area is SEMI-DETACHED and BUNGALOWS. The least common houses are MAISONETTES. The age of housing in this area varies because a lot of new houses are being built in this area. Bungalows are normally the oldest type of housing in the area. Here is a list of the total houses in this area:- Detached 12 Semi-detached 264 Terraced 28 Bungalow 162 Maisonettes 3 Flats 5 blocks
Most of the houses in this area are privately owned.
by Martin Champness SANDERS DRAPER.
